{"tid":1681503,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[純推論]今次屯門催淚毒氣事件會唔會係解放軍引致？","createTime":"2019-10-29T12:52:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T13:05:14.000Z","uid":121869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b1afa1e136673f07392cc077f4063be4c8f865cb","tid":1681503,"uid":121869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T12:52:42.000Z","msg":"//<br />\n#純推論<br />\n<br />\n睇電話個陣，有人講返九七年都試過警察同懲教，演練催淚彈，因為風向問題而影響天水圍居民個陣，我就不禁諗&hellip;&hellip;(更正返係天水圍受影響，該演習係警察同懲教合演。)<br />\n<br />\n今次會唔會係重蹈覆轍，而正正青山靶場就係上風位，而依家嘅青山靶場係解放軍使用，有無可能係解放軍演習，無顧及風向而大規模使用催淚彈？因為係廣東嘅解放軍，近期都演習使用催淚彈，而且駐港解放軍喺市區軍營都演習鎮壓行動，我唔排除其實今次係解放軍引致。<br />\n<br />\n以上青山靶場演習係推測，無太多實質證據，<strong>但如果有下白泥居民，或行緊菠蘿山嘅人，提供資料就好。</strong><br />\n<br />\n當然，我都接受唔到黑警咁樣對待屯門居民，係建生亂咁射催淚彈，甚至闖入私人民居，刻意攻擊住宅。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1625821230964324/posts/2487397058140066?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1625821230964324%2Fposts%2F2487397058140066%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg2WYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=523e0f77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1625821230964324/posts/2487397058140066?sfns=mo</a><br />\n//<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201909/27/P2019092500479.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201909%2F27%2FP2019092500479.htm&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg2WYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=5fde9fd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201909/27/P2019092500479.htm</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fuiRiZW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfuiRiZW.jpg&h=863e9321&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100000132953830/posts/2966966119984457?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100000132953830%2Fposts%2F2966966119984457%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg2WYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=4af95eb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100000132953830/posts/2966966119984457?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"576527f3023aeff6e3ce60218c615a18a74ca13c","tid":1681503,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T12:53:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jc8536k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJc8536k.jpg&h=6d7fb408&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"54c81959311f24e93b521605b4e08ad87cc7faca","tid":1681503,"uid":298270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T13:05:14.000Z","msg":"但係琴日 有人拍到呢張<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dGFwi4A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdGFwi4A.png&h=cef30270&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}